Package de.espirit.firstspirit.server.mediamanagement.exif

Interface ExifTags.CasioType2

  • Enclosing interface:
    ExifTags
    public static interface ExifTags.CasioType2
    Definition of specialized Casio Exif tags.

    For further descriptions, tags see http://www.exif.org/Exif2-2.PDF or the manufacturer definitions.

    Since:
    5.0.100
